  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the present study was to investigate the effect of Physical Therapy (PT) on pain
      and mandibular function in patients with anterior disc displacement without reduction (ADD-R)
      or &quot;closed lock&quot; of the TMJ and this in a randomized controlled trial design.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The study evaluated the effect of extra, technical PT over the traditional information on the
      benign nature of the disease and the advice to refrain from overuse or misuse of the
      masticatory system as in parafunctions.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
